{"tid":2530921,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"前華姐冠軍凌緣庭4280萬入市擎天半島,呎價31774","createTime":"2021-05-14T20:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T20:44:32.000Z","uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"69fa62466a35116562a58bd065e07bbdda8f657f","tid":2530921,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:44:32.000Z","msg":"豪宅市場錄名人入市個案，根據土地註冊處資料，九龍站擎天半島1座中層D室，實用面積1347平方呎，上月底以4280萬元成交，呎價約31774元。<br />\n<br />\n新買家凌緣庭(LENG YEN THEAN)早於1991年第三屆國際華裔小姐獲得冠軍殊榮，惟獲獎後她沒有在娛樂圈發展，反而選擇在房地產界發展其事業，以往屬劉鑾雄「大劉」旗下的華人置業，專責售樓及租務的工作，並有傳她一度是「大劉」愛將。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2015/08/19/php1lkO6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2015%2F08%2F19%2Fphp1lkO6B.jpg&h=2b4451c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2502349/org/8c62fdc53a69233f293657568e00c117.jpg/pY-avilgY0ZkysWj-mCKUSumBwsN181iDzfN0w83zdM?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2502349%2Forg%2F8c62fdc53a69233f293657568e00c117.jpg%2FpY-avilgY0ZkysWj-mCKUSumBwsN181iDzfN0w83zdM%3Fv%3Dw960&h=d24747d8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}